## Hotel Invetory Upload [/hotel-inventory]

### Upload New Invetory [POST]

You can upload inventory for any day with any room type, any capacity,
any price.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "hotel": "http://booking-api.windingtree.com/hotels/7f0ddae0ac541bd1",
            "min_guests": 1,
            "max_guests": 2,
            "room_type": "Double Queen Bed",
            "rooms_available": 10,
            "date": "2017-05-05",
            "price": 120,
            "currency": "USD",
            "amenities": []
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /upload-inventory/a68da69c5644ec70

    + Body

            {
                "hotel": "http://booking-api.windingtree.com/hotels/7f0ddae0ac541bd1",
                "min_guests": 1,
                "max_guests": 2,
                "room_type": "Double Queen Bed",
                "rooms_available": 10,
                "date": "2017-05-05",
                "price": 120,
                "currency": "USD",
                "amenities": []
            }

